config RAETH
        tristate "Ralink GMAC"
        ---help---
          This driver supports Ralink gigabit ethernet family of
          adapters.

config RAETH_ASUS_N65U_OBJ
        bool "Use raeth driver hacked by ASUS (route local TX traffic via PPE). Buggy."
        depends on RAETH
        ---help---
          This driver from RT-N65U, used 1xRGMII scheme, boost USB3 TX speed up to 35 MB/s,
          boost USB2 TX speed up to 20 MB/s. Driver is unofficial (non-Ralink/MTK), used 
          tricks and hacks by ASUS. Driver has no sources, based on old Ralink codebase 
          raeth 2.0, route all local TX traffic to PPE. Still buggy. Caused tx_ring full 
          issue, NETDEV_WATCHDOG issue.

config PDMA_NEW
        bool
	default y if  (RALINK_MT7620 || RALINK_MT7621)
        depends on RAETH

config RAETH_SCATTER_GATHER_RX_DMA
        bool
	default y if (RALINK_MT7620 || RALINK_MT7621)
        depends on RAETH


